{"tid":757526,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近3年逾百警員被捕　休班警佔大半","createTime":"2018-07-27T02:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T03:10:04.000Z","uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f88b4bb5682a48214742be32b3ce69c6f0ef91","tid":757526,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:30:56.000Z","msg":"警務人員操守近年備受關注。警務署回覆立法會財委會議員的數據顯示，2015至2017年每年分別有35、43及29名警員被捕，當中各年分別有22、33及23名屬休班警。全體被捕警員中，這三年分別有19、34及18人是被警方拘捕。此外，每年分別有16、9及11名警員被其他執法部門拘捕，例如廉政公署及海關。<br />\n<br />\n被警方拘捕的警員中，2015至2017年分別各有15、21及15人，涉嫌干犯警隊定義為罪行性質屬較嚴重的刑事案件，當中19人涉嫌在公眾地方行為不檢／打鬥、刑事毀壞及破壞公眾體統、遊蕩等罪行，有7人涉嫌傷人及嚴重毆打、6人涉嫌雜項盜竊。涉嫌非禮、詐騙或店舖盜竊的，各有5人；涉嫌強姦、襲警、刑事恐嚇或車輛內盜竊，則各有1人。"},{"pid":"85423ab856075ebdf0ae90f506ba427a8b2a2294","tid":757526,"uid":105366,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:31:49.000Z","msg":"最多罪犯既行業"},{"pid":"1c24a7b2ac1f9cee09e2edb8e543bfd5063ac152","tid":757526,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:32:52.000Z","msg":"唔係點請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f39abc852ac9d25500f351125e29603df5ac5c0","tid":757526,"uid":135409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"唔係每個警察都係壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6705429b75555495c4f0aac0d44e0d41c14b5c0d","tid":757526,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28eecbd5df6d4bacb32f9e37300e1598b484268","tid":757526,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"黑警聯賽冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1429772f4d2c1ff64a07997cd075b29b3866a2","tid":757526,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eserv